Kuthiwa le ndoda iveze ukuthi yayizifake yona lobu buhlalu ngesikhathi izitika ngefilimu yocansi yabona bekwenza kuyo ifilimu nayo yasika iphethini. Odokotela bathi basebenze kanzima ngamathuluzi abo beza ukuhlenga le ndoda ebibonaka ukuthi ithwele kanzima kumphambili wayo izwa izinhlungu. Kuthiwa ichaze yathi ibizitshela ukuthi kuzoba lula ukukhipha lobu buhlalu kanti ayibuzanga elangeni. Kuthiwa lobu buhlalu obebuhlanganiswe ngento esantambo ubude bayo bebucela ku-17cm. Kuthiwa amabhola obuhlalu abengu-34 iwagqisha emgudwini ohamba umchamo kanti sizosuka isidumo isifuna ukuwakhipha. Kuthiwa ngisho odokotela besithombe bakhuze babaza isithombe sibavezela amabhola obuhlali ekhandelene phakathi endukwini yalo mlisa. Kuthiwa nodokotela obesebenza lolu daba umeme abanye ababili ukuba bazombonisa lo mhlolo, baphinde bamsize ukuze ubuhlalu bukhishwe ngempumelelo kungabi nokulimala ngoba indawo ebucayi abebeyisebenza. Kuthiwa isigameko esifana nalesi sesike senzeka umfana oneminyaka engu-11 naye efaka amabholana amancane ebuntwini bakhe ezigangela nje kanti kuzoba nenkinga. - The Daily Mail